About this item

  • Immersive Audio with 50mm Drivers: The S12 Wired Stereo Gaming Headset features 50mm speaker drivers that deliver powerful bass and clear highs, providing an immersive audio experience for your gaming sessions.
  • Wide Frequency Range: With a frequency range of 20-20KHz, the S12 ensures a balanced and detailed sound spectrum, perfect for accurately hearing in-game sounds and music.
  • Dynamic RGB LED Effect: Enhance your gaming setup with the S12's dynamic RGB LED lighting, offering a personalized touch and adding to the overall gaming ambiance.
  • Versatile Compatibility: Connect the S12 to a variety of devices with its USB + 3.5mm + 4Pin headset interface, ensuring compatibility with Xbox One, PS5, Switch, PC, and Laptop.
  • Comfort and Durability: Enjoy the comfort of over-ear design and the freedom of movement with a 2m cable length, making the S12 perfect for extended gaming sessions without discomfort.

    What's in the box

    • Product Description

    Meet the S12 Game Headset, your new gaming companion for an immersive audio experience.
    With 50mm speakers, it offers deep bass and clear highs, covering a wide frequency range of 20-20KHz.
    The headset's dynamic RGB LED effect adds a vibrant touch to your gaming setup.
    Compatible with Xbox One, PS5, Switch, PC, and Laptop, it features a versatile interface: USB + 3.5mm + 4Pin, ensuring easy connectivity.
    The built-in microphone with dimensions of 6.0*2.7mm and a sensitivity of -42dB ±3dB provides clear communication. With a 2m cable, you have the freedom to move during intense gaming sessions.
    Elevate your gaming with the S12's powerful audio and stylish design.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Product Description

    Meet the S12 Game Headset, your new gaming companion for an immersive audio experience. With 50mm speakers, it offers deep bass and clear highs, covering a wide frequency range of 20-20KHz. The headset's dynamic RGB LED effect adds a vibrant touch to your gaming setup. The built-in microphone with dimensions of 6.0*2.7mm and a sensitivity of -42dB ±3dB provides clear communication. With a 2m cable, you have the freedom to move during intense gaming sessions. Elevate your gaming with the S12's powerful audio and stylish design.
